Package: rigakuXRD
Type: Package
Title: X-Ray Diffraction Data Import and Analysis 
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Gredig", email = "tgredig@csulb.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5824-7626"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <tgredig@csulb.edu>
Description: This package imports x-ray diffraction and reflectivity 
  data in various common data formats. It assists with peak analysis. 
  This includes fitting peak position and width to determine crystal
  size or thin film thickness. 
URL: https://github.com/thomasgredig/rigakuXRD
